decade: 1980s
concept_type: framework
date_introduced: 1993
originator: Stuart Kauffman
significance: foundational
tags: cas, evolution
notes:            NK model; rugged landscapes; adaptive walks; trade-off between evolvability and optimization
```

```
id:               edge_of_chaos
