domain: core_complexity
decade: 1980s
concept_type: principle
date_introduced: 1990
originator: Christopher Langton
significance: major
tags: cas, computation
notes:            Computation and adaptation are maximized at the phase transition between order and chaos
```

```
id:               dissipative_structures
